Purpose

To evaluate energy expenditure and other parameters in muscle Tsc1 knockout mice. This script was most recently updated on Mon Feb 4 15:09:10 2019.

Experimental Details

Mice were run in the CLAMS in several batches, and combined.

Raw Data

Sample Key

Oxymax Input

There are two batches of data, baseline and after 3 months of diet.
